name: Dystopian Hours IV- Failure
description:
Monumento ai Partigiani is the final scene of this universe, it’s where Failure starts lurking, trying to hunt you down. It will make you doubt yourself, telling you that you are not good enough, that you are not going to make it to the top, and even if you do, do you even deserve to be there or are you a fraud? But what did I say in the beginning of our dark journey? There’s always hope and light as long as you look hard enough…

Did you get out of this universe alive? Or are you still here?
